replies.body:
I've found that a {{item:3070}}  as first buy is a massive QoL improvement. 1/10 junglers gives up their blue buff before 20 minutes (in my experience), so you can never count on that. If you're leveling E first, {{item:3165}}  just won't cut it for regen early on.

After you cap CDR, finish {{item:3003}}  or  {{item:3040}}  then {{item:3135}}  or {{item:3089}} 

With the upcoming AP changes, {{item:3003}}  is your strongest first AP item.
